---
---
<section id="pilares" class="py-32 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center bg-white">
  <div class="mb-24">
    <h2 class="font-outfit text-[44px] text-slate-900 font-light tracking-[-0.02em] leading-[1.2] mb-6">
      Pilares de Desarrollo
    </h2>
    <p class="font-inter text-[15px] font-light text-slate-600 leading-[1.7] max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-80">
      El enfoque integral de Coopetour para asegurar un futuro próspero y sostenible.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-start gap-16 md:gap-24">
    
    <!-- Pilar 1 -->
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center group w-full md:w-1/3 cursor-default">
      <div class="mb-8 text-slate-900 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:text-[#FF6600] transition-all duration-700 transform group-hover:-translate-y-3">
        <svg fill="none" height="64" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="64">
          <path d="M6.5 12c.94-3.46 4.94-6 8.5-6 3.56 0 6.06 2.54 7 6-.94 3.47-3.44 6-7 6s-7.56-2.53-8.5-6Z"></path>
          <path d="M18 12v.01"></path>
          <path d="M11.52 17c-2.28 1.7-5.52 2.5-8.52 2.5-1.28-4.28 0-8.28 3.5-11.5"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-inter text-[12px] font-medium tracking-[0.15em] text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">
        Producción Pesquera
      </h3>
      <p class="font-inter text-[14px] text-slate-600 font-light leading-relaxed opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700">
        Fomentando prácticas de pesca sostenible que protegen las especies locales y aseguran el sustento de las familias.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Pilar 2 -->
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center group w-full md:w-1/3 cursor-default">
      <div class="mb-8 text-slate-900 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:text-[#FF6600] transition-all duration-700 transform group-hover:-translate-y-3">
        <svg fill="none" height="64" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="64">
          <path d="M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z"></path>
          <path d="M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-inter text-[12px] font-medium tracking-[0.15em] text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">
        Conservación del Mangle
      </h3>
      <p class="font-inter text-[14px] text-slate-600 font-light leading-relaxed opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700">
        Protección activa de los ecosistemas de manglar, vitales para la biodiversidad y la resiliencia costera.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Pilar 3 -->
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center group w-full md:w-1/3 cursor-default">
      <div class="mb-8 text-slate-900 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:text-[#FF6600] transition-all duration-700 transform group-hover:-translate-y-3">
        <svg fill="none" height="64" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="64">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
          <path d="M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20"></path>
          <path d="M2 12h20"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-inter text-[12px] font-medium tracking-[0.15em] text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">
        Turismo y Entretenimiento
      </h3>
      <p class="font-inter text-[14px] text-slate-600 font-light leading-relaxed opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700">
        Organización de torneos de pesca y recorridos ecológicos que atraen visitantes y dinamizan la economía local.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
